{
  "stem": "4570.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, they took that private bank away from the family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They still had the block of flat where-- where they had the apartment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we knew that it's-- it's getting worse than better.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when-- when Goldie got-- it-- it was-- his number was 507.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he and his brother were both in that transport.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I just-- I-- it-- I only had a year and a 1/2 with him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I was heartbroken that he went away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when he went away, it was in winter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in December.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I just couldn't bear to be in-- in a warm bed and to have a good meal, because I-- I was just frantic thinking that he will be cold.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He will be hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And eventually, there must have been more women or girls in my position.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and some, obviously, were much smarter than I, and older.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they started to go into to ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The ghetto was still not divided.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were still Czech families living there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the Jews were only in the army barracks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the women got into the ghettos to see their boyfriend.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so eventually, I found out that Goldie had arranged for me to come and where to meet him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "At that time, the train didn't go into Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It went to a little township by Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know how long it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You had to walk on-- on the road about 1/2 an hour, 3/4 an hour.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- I was-- I was frightened, but I was also very excited.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and I went to his mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, look.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Get as much food on the black market I can-- that I can carry.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'm-- I'm meeting Goldie.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she says, oh, don't go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Don't go.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
